{
  "name": "Bot Admisión — Async DB",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ASYNC DB — Escrituras en Postgres\n\nWorkflow independiente que recibe el payload del flujo principal\n**después** de que el mensaje ya fue enviado al usuario.\n\nNo bloquea al usuario. Si falla, el Error Handler captura\ny manda a la DLQ.\n\n**Payload que recibe** (body del POST):\n```json\n{\n  \"remote_jid\":       \"5491112345678\",\n  \"whatsapp_name\":    \"Juan\",\n  \"message_id\":       \"MSGID\",\n  \"user_text\":        \"hola\",\n  \"bot_message\":      \"Bienvenido...\",\n  \"current_step_id\":  \"INICIO\",\n  \"next_step_id\":     \"PASO_1\",\n  \"message_type_out\": \"text\",\n  \"is_new_user\":      true\n}\n```\n\n**Para conectar:** copiar la URL del webhook de este workflow\ny usarla en el nodo `HTTP — Trigger Async DB` del flujo principal.",
        "height": 448,
        "width": 600,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "e66991ff-c984-4e63-a132-8a27e3fdf803",
      "name": "README Async DB",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        192,
        272
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "async-db",
        "responseMode": "lastNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "e664ff1a-1933-4021-8999-5c6f951694f4",
      "name": "Webhook — Async DB",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        272,
        752
      ],
      "webhookId": "async-db"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Normalizar el payload: el body puede venir anidado en .body (n8n webhook)\n// o directo en el json root\nconst raw = $input.first().json;\nconst p = raw.body || raw;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    remote_jid:       p.remote_jid       || '',\n    whatsapp_name:    p.whatsapp_name    || '',\n    message_id:       p.message_id       || '',\n    user_text:        p.user_text        || '',\n    bot_message:      p.bot_message      || '',\n    current_step_id:  p.current_step_id  || 'INICIO',\n    next_step_id:     p.next_step_id     || 'FIN',\n    message_type_out: p.message_type_out || 'text',\n    is_new_user:      p.is_new_user === true || p.is_new_user === 'true'\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "7e1e16bf-58f1-48ee-a5e8-a75c7174e797",
      "name": "Code — Normalizar Payload",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        496,
        752
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "new-user",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.is_new_user }}",
              "rightValue": true,
              "operator": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "operation": "true"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "603e0172-c904-4cc4-9531-36e36bf5b8ac",
      "name": "IF — Usuario Nuevo",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        720,
        752
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "executeQuery",
        "query": "INSERT INTO users\n  (remote_jid, whatsapp_name, status, created_at, updated_at)\nVALUES ($1, $2, 'nuevo', NOW(), NOW())\nON CONFLICT (remote_jid)\nDO UPDATE SET\n  whatsapp_name = EXCLUDED.whatsapp_name,\n  updated_at    = NOW()\nRETURNING id, remote_jid, status",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "6d2cad1b-3c4c-43ed-9f39-37c9468b46f2",
      "name": "Postgres — INSERT Usuario",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        944,
        592
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "executeQuery",
        "query": "UPDATE users\nSET updated_at = NOW()\nWHERE remote_jid = $1\nRETURNING id, remote_jid, status",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b938ae67-5334-4311-8e84-c5737beb6fbe",
      "name": "Postgres — UPDATE Usuario",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        944,
        912
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "executeQuery",
        "query": "INSERT INTO conversations\n  (remote_jid, step_id, user_message, bot_response, message_type, created_at)\nVALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, NOW())",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "1b36ae2e-66a6-473a-9c61-c0647c0e264b",
      "name": "Postgres — INSERT Conversación",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2,
